rows.label: qst202201_msg003
rows.name:
My zappy powers are super awesome,
right?

rows.label: qst202201_msg004
rows.name:
Oh, definitely. I only have to stand
next to you to feel my hairs standing
on end!

rows.label: qst202201_msg006
rows.name:
I'm always giving it my all,
so my power's like, always
overflowing too.

rows.label: qst202201_msg007
rows.name: It uh...it doesn't bug you or anything?

rows.label: qst202201_msg008
rows.name:
I guess maybe I am a little scared
sometimes that I might touch you by
accident and get myself zapped...

rows.label: qst202201_msg009
rows.name:
But it's not really that much of a deal,
I don't think.

rows.label: qst202201_msg010
rows.name:
But how am I supposed to control
my powers if I'm always releasing
them at full blast?

rows.label: qst202201_msg011
rows.name:
I wish I could be more like Homura-san. 
She's got hers under control...

rows.label: qst202201_msg012
rows.name:
Now, don't be like that, Raiko.
I think you're very charming in
your own unique way.

rows.label: qst202201_msg013
rows.name:
Yeah! Everything's a whole lot brighter
when you're around, Raiko!

rows.label: qst202201_msg014
rows.name:
Isn't that just because my lightning's
illuminating the place...?

rows.label: qst202201_msg015
rows.name:
Nu-uh. You're cute as a button and
you're fun to be around. You really
cheer us all up.

rows.label: qst202201_msg018
rows.name:
I feel like the only thing I'm good at
right now is fighting...
